fileinfo.description: This file contains the latest measurements from NRPAs monitoring network Radnett. Timestamp refers to the time when this data was generated (in UTC). This file is updated 30 minutes passed each hour. This is the same time as official page http://radnett.nrpa.no is updated. Your application must cache the data for 30 minutes. Misuse may cause blocking of the requesting IP.

resource.name: Radnett
resource.description: National gamma dose rate early warning network.

operator.name: Norwegian Radiation and Nuclear Safety Authority
